  m_text: 'Control panel holds all actions player can do in a battle. On the far
    left is just an icon with member name, followed by player''s chosen skills. On
    the far right, player can speed up time, stop time altogether, or open options
    panel. You can also pass a turn if you can''t use other skills or simply don''t
    wanna play this turn.


    After you select a skill, you need to confirm by
    clicking the member you wanna target


'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ea3febd2a652e944cbc6ba9ae7d35fed, type: 2}
