  m_text: 'Fights consist of rounds. In each round, every member has one turn. On
    turn, members can use one skill. Member currently on turn has a blue indicator
    bellow them.


    On the left are your members that you control. On the right
    are enemy members controllled by AI


    Each member has a health bar above
    them displaying health and current status effects.'
